profile:
We consult with you on your exterior home project needs and provide you with options from a variety of manufacturers that fit your budget. We are your turn key solution.

The process of changing your windows and doors has not changed in the past 75 years. Most people call 3 window companies and get each of them to provide a quote. This means that you get 3 sales representatives coming to your home, taking measurements and providing you an estimate and then asking you to buy. This also means that you need to spend at least 3 hours with them and try and figure out which of the estimates is right for you.

If you need to repair any part of your exterior home the traditional method is to call different experts and then deal with them all separately, a time consuming job, not to mention that you don’t know if you are dealing with a reputable firm. The Home Zone has assembled the best in the respective industries and allows you to deal with one person. We manage your entire project and in the end save you time, money and the headaches of trying to manage the different trades people.
